# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:434
msgid ""
"Add text captions on top of your video. We support both VTT (WebVTT) and "
"SubRip (SRT) subtitle file formats. These formats are used to display "
"captions or subtitles in videos. They allow you to add text-based subtitles "
